!! Versions and updating
You might want to delete tiddlers that override shadow tiddlers in the plugin. Go to the control panel, fold out the plugin using the down-arrow icon and open the contents tab. Tiddlers in bold are o.k. Tiddlers with names in normal style are dangerous and you might have to delete them to get the new version from the updated plugin.


!!! Version 1.2.15
