*** you can leave the translation empty to save the space
* independent save button (no longer a duplication of the core save button, so [[adding an accesskey to the core version|https://groups.google.com/forum/#!msg/tiddlywiki/OJQ0yRq4zog/DqCXRmWxAgAJ]] should not be a problem anymore)
